ng%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20meeting%20new%20people%20with%20different%20backgrounds%20and%20wide%2C%20varying%20perspectives%20on%20life%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20faith.%20Because%20of%20my%20nomadic%20lifestyle%20and%20audacious%20personality%2C%20I%20would%20quickly%20and%20easily%20allow%20people%20into%20my%20inner%20circle%20like%20water%20flowing%20in%2C%20uninhibited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20an%20insatiable%20desire%20for%20unique%20experiences%20and%20a%20multifaceted%20community%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20cost.%20Throughout%20that%20time%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20excusing%20behaviors%20in%20friends%20that%20hurt%20me%20or%20others%20around%20them%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20speaking%20up%20when%20I%20should%20have%20because%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftherapists-share-what-people-pleaser-clients-talk-about-relationship-issues-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople-pleasing%20habit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad17a58f-f938-4e43-9f7a-86df4df74f9b%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20learn%20how%20to%20create%20healthy%20boundaries%20from%20my%20parents%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20raised%20in%20a%20household%20that%20modeled%20healthy%20boundaries%20or%20welcomed%20difficult%20conversations.%20I%20was%20taught%20to%20be%20amenable%20and%20not%20to%20question%20authority%2C%20even%20when%20injustice%20was%20being%20done.%20Thus%2C%20I%20wasn't%20equipped%20to%20deal%20with%20certain%20interpersonal%20challenges%20when%20they%20inevitably%20arrived%20in%20adulthood.%20I%20continued%20the%20pattern%20of%20sweeping%20big%2C%20important%20things%20under%20the%20rug%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20not%20ruffling%20feathers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20therapy%2C%20I've%20learned%20how%20to%20set%20boundaries%20in%20both%20new%20and%20old%20relationships%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20to%20pass%20these%20hard-learned%20lessons%20down%20to%20my%20daughters%2C%20even%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20For%20e