e%20of%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20young%20people%20looking%20to%20test%20their%20entrepreneurial%20mettle%20through%20the%20world%20of%20so-called%20search%20funds.%20Sometimes%20described%20as%20mini-private%20equity%20or%20entrepreneurship%20through%20acquisition%2C%20a%20search%20fund%20is%20a%20small%20investment%20fund%20run%20by%20one%20or%20two%20people%20established%20to%20buy%20an%20existing%20small%20business.%20Once%20the%20business%20is%20purchased%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bsearchers%26quot%3B%20run%20it%20with%20an%20eye%20toward%20creating%20value%20by%20streamlining%20operations%20and%20growing%20in%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.novastone-ca.com%2Fdocs%2F2024_Stanford_Search_Fund_Study.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Stanford%20Business%20School%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20search%20fund%20creation%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%20in%202023%2C%20the%20latest%20year%20with%20data%2C%20with%20more%20than%2090%20first-time%20search%20funds%20raised.%20The%20strategy%20is%20particularly%20hot%20among%20young%20people%2C%20with%20Stanford%20finding%20that%20nearly%2080%25%20of%20first-time%20fundraisers%20in%202023%20clocked%20in%20at%2035%20or%20younger%2C%20including%20many%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmba-graduates-cant-find-jobs-white-collar-hiring-slowdown-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20freshly%20graduated%20MBAs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20searchers%2C%20like%20Froendt%2C%20are%20so%20eager%20to%20be%20their%20own%20boss%20that%20they%20forgo%20outside%20investments%20%E2%80%94%20using%20their%20personal%20savings%20or%20their%20spouse's%20income%20to%20fund%20their%20entrepreneurial%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boom%20in%20search%20funds%20is%20partly%20a%20response%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-slowdown-careers-impact-private-credit-portfolio-operations-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20more%20complicated%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-slump-professional-white-collar-jobs-recession-high-salary-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhite-collar%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20once%20the%20obvious%20pathway%20to%20success%2C%20feel%20less%20stable.%20The%20dream%20of%20entrepreneurship%20is%20still%20alive%20and%20well%2C%20but%20tech%20startups%20can%20feel%20out%20of%20reach%20given%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-industry-amazon-microsoft-meta-google-companies-intensity-hardcore-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenormous%20shadow%20tech%20giants%20like%20Google%20and%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20cast%20over%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESearch%20funds%20and%20their%20various%20cousins%20offer%20a%20more%20realistic%20path%20to%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20romantic%20entrepreneurial%20belief%20that%20you%20can%20only%20succeed%20by%20starting%20a%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Newton%20Campos%2C%20professor%20of%20entrepreneurship%20at%20IE%20University%20in%20Madrid%20and%20the%20founding%20partner%20of%20Newton%20Equity%20Partners%2C%20a%20recently%20launched%20fund%20that%20invests%20in%20search%20funds%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFroendt%2C%20who%20was%20bitten%20by%20the%20entrepreneurial%20bug%20running%20a%20car%20wash%20in%20high%20school%2C%20calls%20it%20%26quot%3Bbetting%20on%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraditionally%20entrepreneurship%20is%20thought%20of%20as%20%26quot%3Bzero-to-one%2C%26quot%3B%20involving%20brand%20new%20ideas%20starting%20at%20the%20ground%20floor%2C%26quot%3B%20Froendt%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20eyes%20opened%20to%20the%20thought%20of%20being%20an%20entrepreneur%20in%20the%20context%20of%20an%20existing%20business%2C%20it%20immediately%20resonated%20with%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why%20some%20of%20the%20brightest%20young%20people%20are%20choosing%20to%20buy%20and%20operate%20unglamorous%20businesses%20like%20porta-potty%20rentals%20(yes%2C%20really)%20instead%20of%20climbing%20the%20corporate%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221390%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20blue%20suit%20smiles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec431763d72727e198e15a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221130%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdam%20Froendt%3Cp%3EAdam%20Froendt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221fbb08ee-fe7b-446a-9138-d814be2ef9f0%5C%22%3EHow%20search%20funds%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20search%20fund%20model%2C%20created%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20begins%20with%20an%20entrepreneur%20finding%20investors%20to%20fund%20their%20salary%20and%20expenses%20during%20a%20multi-year%20search%20for%20a%20business%20worth%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFroendt%20is%20taking%20a%20higher-risk%20and%20higher-reward%20path%20by%20self-funding%20his%20search%2C%20which%20takes%2C%20on%20average%2C%20two%20years.%20This%20model%20offers%20more%20flexibility%20over%20the%20businesses%20targeted%2C%20as%20well%20as%20more%20control%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20more%20equity.%20As%20the%20founder%20of%20TrueGrit%20Capital%2C%20Froendt%20will%20be%20living%20off%20his%20%26quot%3Bown%20personal%20balance%20sheet%26quot%3B%20(his%20savings)%20for%20up%20to%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20is%20to%20buy%20a%20successful%20small%20business%2C%20often%20from%20an%20owner-operator%20looking%20to%20retire.%20Froendt%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20company%20with%20between%20%243%20million%20and%20%2412%20million%20in%20yearly%20revenue%20located%20between%20Maryland%20and%20South%20Carolina%20and%20in%20the%20healthcare%20services%20(think%20home%20health%20or%20care%20management)%2C%20financial%20services%20(think%20insurance%20or%20accounting)%2C%20or%20knowledge%20(think%20training%20or%20certification)%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20searchers'%20goals%20are%20to%20streamline%20operations%2C%20grow%20revenue%2C%20and%20create%20value%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20shareholders.%20Most%20searchers%20plan%20to%20exit%20after%20five%20or%20more%20years%2C%20though%20some%20plan%20to%20hold%20indefinitely%2C%20which%20is%20what%20Froendt%20hopes%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20payout%20can%20be%20massive.%20According%20to%20the%20Stanford%20study%2C%20the%20average%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Froi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereturn%20on%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20search%20funds%20studied%20was%20four%20and%20a%20half%20times%20invested%20capital%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emuch%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20a%20traditional%20private%20equity%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20similarities%20to%20private%20equity%2C%20causing%20some%20to%20call%20the%20model%20%26quot%3Bmini%20private%20equity.%26quot%3B%20But%20Peter%20Kelly%2C%20a%20lecturer%20at%20Stanford%20Graduate%20School%20of%20Business%20who%20conducts%20the%20biannual%20survey%20and%20who%20ran%20a%20successful%20search%20fund%20business%20in%20home%20health%20care%2C%20said%20the%20terminology%20is%20inaccurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%2C%20who%20prefers%20the%20phrase%20entrepreneurship%20through%20acquisition%2C%20said%20that%20the%20model%20borrows%20from%20private%20equity%20financing%20but%20is%20fueled%20by%20the%20entrepreneur's%20desire%20to%20become%20an%20owner-manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20of%20a%20private%20equity%20fund%20gets%20paid%20through%20fees%2C%20incentivizing%20them%20to%20grow%20their%20assets%20under%20management%2C%20he%20said.%20A%20searcher%20is%20a%20direct%20investor%20(usually%20the%20largest)%20and%20gets%20paid%20by%20growing%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA.J.%20Wasserstein%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20at%20the%20Yale%20School%20of%20Business%20put%20it%20this%20way%3A%20%26quot%3BSearch%20is%20about%20jumping%20into%20a%20CEO%20role%20and%20leading%20and%20building.%20Private%20equity%20is%20about%20providing%20capital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bbf016b-72c1-485c-bdf7-3ca99a6d2927%5C%22%3EWhy%20it's%20growing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESearch%20funds%20were%20developed%20in%20the%20MBA%20world%2C%20and%20some%20of%20its%20popularity%20can%20be%20traced%20to%20an%20ever-growing%20list%20of%20courses%20about%20the%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECampos%20counts%2025%20schools%20that%20teach%20it%20worldwide%20but%20said%20he%20expects%20the%20number%20to%20reach%20100%20in%20just%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20interest%20in%20search%20funds%20grows%2C%20more%20firms%2C%20including%20Pacific%20Lake%20Partners%20and%20Relay%20Investments%2C%20have%20raised%20funds%20to%20invest%20in%20them.%20Campos%20founded%20his%20own%20investment%20fund%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20help%20institutional%20investors%20find%20search%20funds%20in%20Europe%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECampos%2C%20who%20said%20he%20sold%20a%20rental%20apartment%20to%20invest%2C%20has%20made%2018%20personal%20investments%20in%20search%20funds%2C%20which%20have%20netted%20him%20a%20nice%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWebsites%20like%20SearchFunder%2C%20which%20connects%20investors%20with%20prospective%20searchers%2C%20and%20a%20series%20of%20how-to%20guides%20have%20made%20%26quot%3Bsearching%26quot%3B%20easier%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20Primer%20on%20Search%20Funds%2C%26quot%3B%20updated%20every%20few%20years%20by%20Kelly%20and%20his%20Stanford%20colleagues%2C%20offers%20a%20very%20granular%20guide%20to%20the%20process%2C%20including%20sample%20legal%20documents%20to%20help%20close%20a%20deal.%20Campos%20called%20the%20document%20the%20%26quot%3BBible%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarvard%20professors%20and%20entrepreneurs%20Rocye%20Yudkoff%20and%20Richard%20Ruback%20have%20published%20the%20%26quot%3BHBR%20Guide%20to%20Buying%20a%20Small%20Business%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20essential%20read%20for%20anyone%20interested%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey've%20even%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20podcast%2C%20recently%20discussing%20how%20buying%20a%20successful%20small%20business%20can%20be%20less%20risky%20than%20betting%20on%20a%20career%20with%20a%20large%20corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20institution%20might%20be%20around%20forever%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20around%20forever%20inside%20that%20institution%2C%26quot%3B%20Yudkoff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterest%20in%20search%20funds%20is%20only%20expected%20to%20continue%20as%20tech%20and%20consulting%20firms%20cut%20jobs%20and%20Wall%20Street%20hiring%20slows%20amid%20fears%20of%20an%20economic%20downturn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%2015%25%20of%20the%20Harvard%20Business%20School's%202024%20class%20that%20were%20looking%20for%20jobs%20did%20not%20receive%20any%20job%20offers%20after%20graduation%2C%20compared%20to%20only%204%25%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESearch%20funds%20have%20even%20become%20the%20target%20of%20online%20jokers.%20They%20are%20a%20recurring%20theme%20of%20Search%20Fund%20Stu%2C%20a%20financial%20meme%20maker%20on%20Instagram%20whose%20page%20is%20full%20of%20jokes%20about%20unsexy%20businesses%20like%20port-a-potty%20rentals%20and%20social%20media%20influencers%20promoting%20the%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESearch%20Fund%20Stu%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20is%20operating%20a%20business%20that%20he%20bought%20through%20a%20search%20fund%2C%20and%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20so%20he%20can%20post%20freely.%20One%20of%20his%20posts%20shows%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDBgw2sjP4-E%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephoto%20of%20an%20uncomfortable-looking%20dog%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20labeled%20%26quot%3BMBA%20without%20a%20full-time%20offer%26quot%3B%20and%20riding%20a%20mini-horse%20labeled%20%26quot%3Ba%20%24500k%20search%20fund.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20jokers%2C%20there%20are%20lively%20discussions%20on%20%26quot%3BSMB%20Twitter%2FX%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20current%20operators%20commiserate%20and%20gloat%20about%20the%20highs%20and%20lows%20of%20the%20model%2C%20spawning%20some%20bonafide%20influencer%20stars%2C%20like%20Codie%20Sanchez%2C%20with%20more%20than%20half%20a%20million%20X%20followers%20and%202%20million%20Instagram%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESanchez%20left%20a%20career%20as%20a%20private%20equity%20investor%20to%20buy%20and%20sell%20small%20businesses%20and%20teach%20the%20model%20to%20others%20through%20her%20media%20brand%2C%20Contrarian%20Thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFroendt%20recently%20quit%20social%20media%20but%20said%20that%20Walker%20Deibel%2C%20another%20influencer%20and%20author%20of%20the%20guide%20%26quot%3BBuy%20Then%20Build%2C%26quot%3B%20played%20a%20big%20part%20in%20his%20decision%20to%20try%20out%20the%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20warns%2C%20however%2C%20that%20people%20shouldn't%20jump%20into%20search%20funds%20because%20they%20see%20it%20online.%20They%20are%20still%20quite%20risky%20compared%20to%20climbing%20the%20corporate%20hierarchy%2C%20with%2037%25%20of%20funds%20raised%20failing%20to%20acquire%20a%20company%20and%2031%25%20of%20companies%20acquired%20either%20still%20operating%20or%20having%20exited%20at%20a%20loss%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Stanford%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20try%20not%20to%20promote%20it%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20care%20if%20my%20students%20do%20it%2C%20I%20just%20want%20them%20to%20learn%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20no%20Stanford%20business%20school%20graduates%20did%20it%20one%20year%2C%20I%20might%20say%2C%20'That's%20too%20bad%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%2030%20graduates%20did%20it%2C%20that%20would%20make%20me%20nervous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsearch-funds-mini-private-equity-how-to-job-market-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743584402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec539469253ccddf9af3e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsearch-funds-mini-private-equity-how-to-job-market-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MBAs%20are%20increasingly%20turning%20to%20search%20funds%2C%20which%20buy%20and%20grow%20small%20businesses%2C%20to%20test%20their%20entrepreneurial%20mettle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22anicoll%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Nicoll)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsearch-funds-mini-private-equity-how-to-job-market-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Takeshi%20Kitano%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Kubi%E2%80%99%20to%20Open%20London%E2%80%99s%20Queer%20East%20Festival%20%E2%80%93%20Global%20Bulletin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743584320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2FKubi-Japanese-Cinema.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236354692%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CINEMATIC%20CELEBRATION%20Legendary%20Japanese%20director%20Takeshi%20Kitano%E2%80%98s%20samurai%20epic%20%E2%80%9CKubi%E2%80%9D%20will%20open%20the%20sixth%20edition%20of%20London%E2%80%99s%20Queer%20East%20Festival%20on%20April%2023%20at%20BFI%20Southbank.%20The%20festival%2C%20running%20through%20May%2018%2C%20will%20showcase%20over%20100%20titles%20exploring%20LGBTQ%2B%20experiences%20across%20East%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%20Highlights%20include%20%E2%80%9CRookie%2C%E2%80%9D%20about%20a%20teenager%20joining%20an%20all-girls%20volleyball%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3