g%20out%20of%20Russia...That%20would%20be%2C%20that%20if%20you%20buy%20oil%20from%20Russia%2C%20you%20can't%20do%20business%20in%20the%20United%20States...there%20will%20be%20a%2025%25%20tariff%20on%20all%20oil%2C%20a%2025-%20to%2050-point%20tariff%20on%20all%20oil%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20new%20US%20sanctions%20on%20Russian%20energy%20companies%20poses%20the%20risk%20of%20inflation%20in%20developing%20economies%20as%20oil%20prices%20soar%20to%20unprecedented%20levels.%20It%20especially%20poses%20a%20worry%20for%20India%20as%20Moscow%20is%20one%20of%20New%20Delhi's%20biggest%20crude%20oil%20suppliers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20crude%20oil%20imports%20crossed%205%20million%20barrels%20per%20day%20(bpd)%20in%20March%202025%2C%20the%20highest%20monthly%20volume%20in%20over%2015%20years%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20commodity%20market%20analytics%20firm%20Kpler.%20If%20this%2C%20around%2030%20percent%20of%20it%20is%20imported%20from%20Russia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Crude%20Oil%20Imports%20In%20March%202025%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(Source%3A%20Kpler%20data)%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERussia%3A%201%2C864%20thousand%20bpd%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIraq%3A%20920%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESaudi%20Arabia%3A%20565%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUAE%3A%20424%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUS%3A%20289%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENigeria%3A%20222%20%C2%A0thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKuwait%3A%20110%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAngola%3A%20150%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBrazil%3A%2091%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEcuador%3A%2065%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EColumbia%3A%2063%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVenezuela%3A%2061%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECongo%3A%2058%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EQatar%3A%2036%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGhana%3A%2034%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOman%3A%2033%20thousand%20bpd%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Dependency%20On%20Russian%20Oil%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20after%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20India%20has%20reduced%20its%20reliance%20on%20Middle%20Eastern%20and%20African%20oil%20in%20favor%20of%20a%20cheaper%20and%20abundant%20supply%20from%20Moscow.%20Refiners%20have%20enjoyed%20bigger%20profits%20due%20to%20the%20cheaper%20supplies.%20In%20fact%2C%20New%20Delhi's%20crude%20oil%20import%20from%20Moscow%20reached%20an%20eight-month%20high%20in%20March%2C%20despite%20sanctions%20imposed%20on%20Russian%20oil%20entities%20by%20the%20outgoing%20Biden%20administration%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kpler%20data%2C%20India's%20import%20of%20Russian%20crude%20jumped%20to%20around%201.9%20million%20barrels%20per%20day%20(bpd)%20in%20March%20-%20marking%20an%20increase%20of%20480%20thousand%20bpd%20month-on-month%20and%20300%20thousand%20bpd%20year-on-year.%20In%20February%2C%20India%20imported%201.47%20million%20barrels%20of%20crude%20oil%20from%20Russia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Threat%20And%20Oil%20Prices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20remark%20pushed%20benchmark%20futures%20up%2C%20with%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20surging%203.1%20per%20cent%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20biggest%20gain%20in%20almost%2011%20weeks.%20Prices%20slipped%20a%20bit%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20but%20steadied%20in%20thin%20trading%20on%20Wednesday.%20Brent%20futures%20were%20unchanged%20at%20%2474.49%20a%20barrel%20after%20slipping%200.4%20per%20cent%20on%20Tuesday.%20US%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20crude%20futures%20rose%203%20cents%20to%20%2471.23%20after%20dropping%200.4%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happens%20If%20the%20US%20Goes%20Ahead%20With%20Its%20Threat%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerica%20is%20India's%20top%20trading%20partner%2C%20so%20under%20a%20scenario%20of%20%26quot%3Bsecondary%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20for%20buyers%20of%20Russian%20oil%2C%20India's%20oil%20supply%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20adversely%20affected%20and%20New%20Delhi%20may%20have%20to%20look%20for%20alternative%20supplies%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Bloomberg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraditional%20sanctions%20have%20created%20enough%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20quoted%20Warren%20Patterson%2C%20the%20head%20of%20commodities%20strategy%20for%20ING%20Groep%20NV%20in%20Singapore%2C%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20of%20secondary%20tariffs%20only%20intensifies%20this%20uncertainty%2C%20given%20that%20it%20is%20a%20new%20tool.%20Buyers%20need%20to%20decide%20whether%20the%20advantages%20of%20picking%20up%20discounted%20crude%20outweigh%20the%20potential%20hit%20on%20its%20economy%20from%20additional%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Trump's%20threat%20looming%2C%20Indian%20refiners%20have%20rushed%20to%20the%20market%20to%20seek%20crude%20supply.%20The%20Bloomberg%20report%20said%20state-owned%20Bharat%20Petroleum%20Corp%20and%20Hindustan%20Petroleum%20Corp%20are%20seeking%20additional%20supplies%20for%20May%20arrival%20from%20regions%20such%20as%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20North%20Sea%20and%20Mediterranean.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emergence%20of%20such%20prompt%20demand%20for%20non-Russian%20cargoes%20likely%20signals%20concerns%20around%20India's%20ability%20to%20receive%20all%20the%20barrels%20refiners%20had%20earlier%20purchased%20from%20Moscow%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEager%20to%20keep%20importing%20cheap%20crude%20from%20Russia%2C%20oil%20refiners%20in%20India%20have%20been%20working%20with%20merchants%2C%20shippers%20and%20other%20middlemen%20to%20rebuild%20supply%20chains%20following%20Biden's%20sanctions.%20Last%20month%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%20that%20Indian%20refiners%20were%20reconfiguring%20the%20existing%20networks%20with%20selling%20entities%2C%20tankers%20and%20insurance%20providers%20that%20are%20not%20on%20Washington's%20blacklist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20also%20actively%20diversifying%20its%20crude%20sources%20by%20increasing%20imports%20from%20other%20countries%2C%20including%20Angola%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20West%20African%20to%20reduce%20dependency%20on%20Russian%20oil.%20While%20New%20Delhi's%20import%20of%20Russian%20barrels%20increased%2C%20Indian%20refiners%20also%20imported%20two-thirds%20more%20US%20crude%20in%20March%20than%20in%20February.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20imported%20289%2C000%20barrels%20per%20day%20of%20US%20crude%20in%20March%2C%20up%20from%20146%2C000%20bpd%20in%20February%2C%20according%20to%20Kpler%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20believe%20that%20India's%20strategy%20of%20diversifying%20its%20oil%20supplies%20may%20help%20protect%20against%20any%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20question%20is%2C%20will%20these%20repeated%20shocks%20end%20up%20structurally%20reducing%20Indian%20appetite%20for%20Russian%20crude%3F%20I%20have%20my%20doubts%2C%20as%20long%20as%20the%20economics%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20Vandana%20Hari%2C%20founder%20of%20Vanda%20Insights%20in%20Singapore%2C%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bluff%2C%20a%20bargaining%20ploy%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Trump.%20But%20refiners%20need%20to%20prepare%2C%20they%20can't%20rely%20on%20hunches%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20bizarre%20and%20unlikely%20a%20supply%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743581640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F9t16r88o_russia-oil-reuters_625x300_02_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-t