ssessing%20their%20pros%20and%20cons.%20From%20historic%20homes%20dating%20back%20to%20the%2019th%20century%20to%20midcentury%20modern%20homes%20from%20Seattle's%20post-World%20War%20II%20boom%20to%20modern%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuilders-new-construction-rental-homes-investors-price-cuts-mortgage-rates-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20significant%20tradeoff%20to%20be%20made%20when%20choosing%20is%20location%20versus%20home%20size.%20I%20initially%20thought%20of%20a%20short%20commute%20and%20a%20large%20home%20as%20must-haves%2C%20but%20given%20my%20budget%20and%20the%20need%20to%20have%20space%20for%20three%20adults%20and%20three%20dogs%2C%20I%20had%20to%20sacrifice%20on%20the%20length%20of%20my%20commute.%20Many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-mistake-buyers-sellers-mortgage-rates-time-to-buy-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomebuyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20make%20this%20same%20compromise.%20According%20to%20a%20Redfin%20survey%2C%2089%25%20of%20homebuyers%20would%20rather%20purchase%20a%20single-family%20home%20with%20a%20backyard%20than%20a%20unit%20in%20a%20triplex%20with%20a%20shorter%20commute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20we%20focused%20our%20efforts%20on%20West%20Seattle%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20located%20on%20a%20peninsula%20across%20the%20sound%20from%20downtown.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-people-new-york-city-helicopter-commute-avoid-cars-traffic-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommute%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20take%20about%2030%20minutes%20each%20way%20by%20bus%2C%20where%20I%20could%20at%20least%20get%20some%20work%20done%20with%20the%20complimentary%20WiFi.%20This%20was%20a%20decent%20tradeoff%2C%20given%20that%20homes%20in%20West%20Seattle%20were%20about%20%24100%2C000%20less%20than%20h