long%20been%20a%20staple%20of%20the%20hiring%20process%20%E2%80%94%20can%20still%20separate%20the%20good%20developers%20from%20the%20sloppy%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20tools%20keep%20popping%20up%20to%20make%20cheating%20on%20tests%20even%20more%20seamless%3A%20A%20since%20suspended%20Columbia%20University%20student%2C%20Chungin%20%26quot%3BRoy%26quot%3B%20Lee%2C%20recently%20created%20a%20tool%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolumbia-suspends-student-ai-interview-coder-cheat-tool-chungin-lee-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3EInterview%20Coder%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20used%20it%20to%20cheat%20on%20an%20Amazon%20coding%20test%20and%20then%20posted%20the%20interview%20to%20YouTube.%20He's%20selling%20the%20tool%20to%20other%20engineers%20for%20just%20%2460%20a%20month%20(he's%20claimed%20on%20X%20that%20he%20received%20and%20rejected%20an%20internship%20offer).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-stop-people-using-ai-cheat-job-interviews-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3EAmazon%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20said%20candidates%20can%20be%20disqualified%20using%20gen%20AI%20unless%20explicitly%20permitted.%20The%20company%20did%20not%20comment%20specifically%20on%20Lee's%20test%2C%20but%20Margaret%20Callahan%2C%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%2C%20tells%20me%20that%20the%20company%20has%20job%20candidates%20acknowledge%20they%20won't%20use%20gen%20AI%20during%20the%20interview%20process%20when%20it's%20not%20permitted%2C%20but%20it%20does%20have%20them%20share%20their%20history%20of%20working%20with%20the%20tools%20when%20relevant.%20Google%20is%20also%20considering%20bringing%20some%20interviews%20back%20to%20in-person%20settings%2C%20where%20they%20can%20have%20more%20control%20over%20the%20environment.%20A%20Google%20spokesperson%20told%20me%20that%20applicants%