eren't%20being%20watched%20closely%20and%20told%20to%20explain%20their%20work%20as%20they%20went%20%E2%80%94%20confirmation%20that%20some%20engineers%20performed%20worse%20when%20under%20the%20stressful%20conditions%20of%20a%20traditional%20technical%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThese%20interviews%20reward%20test-taking%20over%20engineering%2C%26quot%3B%20Lux%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20ignore%20how%20software%20engineers%20actually%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrej-karpathy-eureka-labs-ai-power-list-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAndrej%20Karpathy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20Open%20AI%20cofounder%2C%20coined%20the%20term%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-software-engineer-skills-jobs-ai-cursor-chatgpt-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evibe%20coding%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20way%20AI%20will%20help%20engineers%20%26quot%3Bjust%20see%20stuff%2C%20say%20stuff%2C%20run%20stuff%2C%20and%20copy-paste%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20have%20it%20%26quot%3Bmostly%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20put%20it.%20An%20engineer's%20skill%20for%20writing%20code%20may%20become%20less%20impressive%20than%20their%20capacity%20to%20understand%20it.%20But%20the%20issue%20hiring%20managers%20tangle%20with%20now%20is%20how%20to%20balance%20the%20benefits%20of%20vibe%20coding%20with%20vetting%20the%20best%20engineers%20from%20large%20pools%20of%20applicants%20in%20a%20tight%20job%20market%20where%20there's%20a%20huge%20incentive%20to%20cheat%20your%20way%20into%20an%20offer%20letter.%20On%20the%20job%2C%20%26quot%3Bhopefully%2C%20they%20are%20using%20AI%2C%20to%20do%20the%20stuff%20AI%20can%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Don%20Jernigan%2C%20a%20vice%20president%20at%20Experis%20Services%2C%20an%20IT%20staffing%20firm.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20be%20testing%20and%20evaluating%20them%20from%20the%20areas%20between%20wha