%3E%20-%20which%20proposes%20changes%20to%20laws%20that%20decide%20how%20Muslim%20charitable%20properties%20are%20administered%20-%20began%20Wednesday%20morning%20with%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fkiren-rijiju%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKiren%20Rijiju%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20the%20opposition%20trading%20jabs%20after%20the%20bill%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20began%20with%20jabs%20at%20the%20Congress%2C%20claiming%20the%20party%20had%20made%20%26quot%3Bquestionable%26quot%3B%20changes%20to%20Waqf%20laws%20when%20in%20power%2C%20including%20the%20denotification%20of%20%26quot%3B123%20major%20buildings...%20given%20to%20the%20Waqf%26quot%3B.%20The%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20have%20given%20the%20Parliament%20to%20the%20Waqf%20if%20not%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20introductory%20speech%20was%20rebutted%20by%20the%20Congress'%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20who%20first%20accused%20Mr%20Rijiju%20of%20making%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%20statements%26quot%3B%20and%20labelled%20the%20Waqf%20amendments%20%26quot%3Ban%20assault%20on%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gogoi%20also%20asked%20why%20the%20Minority%20Affairs%20Ministry%20did%20not%20mention%20this%20bill%20in%20any%20of%20the%20four%20meetings%20of%20its%20parliamentary%20committee%20in%202023%2C%20a%20year%20before%20the%20amendments%20were%20presented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKiren%20Rijiju%20Sets%20Ball%20Rolling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20case%20going%20on%20since%201970%20in%20Delhi%20involved%20several%20properties%2C%20including%20the%20Parliament%20building.%20The%20Delhi%20Waqf%20Board%20had%20claimed%20these...%20the%20case%20was%20in%20court%20but%20then%20the%20UPA%20denotified%20123%20properties%20and%20gave%20them%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Board%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%20on%20the%20'Parliament%20to%20Waqf'%20charge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20After%20introducing%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20says%20%26quot%3BIn%202013%2C%20right%20before%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202014%2C%20there%20were%20some%20steps%20taken%20which%20will%20raise%20questions%20in%20your%20mind.%20In%202013%2C%20the%20act%20was%20changed%20to%20allow%20Sikhs%2C%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6LSe1Wg53D%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6LSe1Wg53D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1907334514780553614%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%202%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20had%20not%20introduced%20this%20amendment%20today%2C%20even%20the%20building%20we%20are%20sitting%20in%20could%20have%20been%20claimed%20as%20Waqf%20property.%20If%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20did%20not%20come%20to%20power...%20several%20other%20properties%20would%20also%20have%20been%20de-notified%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BProperty%20Management%20Issue...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20then%20criticised%20the%20opposition%20for%20standing%20against%20changes%2C%20insisting%20there%20will%20be%20no%20alterations%20to%20the%20management%20of%20mosques%20and%20that%20the%20amendments%20were%20%26quot%3Ba%20property%20management%20issue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20religious%20sentiments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20role%20of%20Waqf%20boards%20is%20to%20supervise%20management%20of%20Waqf%20properties...%20this%20(the%20proposed%20law)%20is%20purely%20a%20provision%20for%20governance%20and%20supervision.%C2%A0It%20is%20simply%20a%20matter%20of%20property%20management.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20fails%20to%20understand%20this%20basic%20distinction...%20or%20chooses%20not%20to...%20I%20have%20no%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20After%20introducing%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20says%20%26quot%3BThe%20provisions%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20management%20of%20any%20mosque%2C%20temple%2C%20or%20religious%20site.%20It%20is%20simply%20a%20matter%20of%20property%20management.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FChEqLgUz8g%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FChEqLgUz8g%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1907339369452564688%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%202%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20government%20had%20removed%20a%20%26quot%3Bdraconian%20provision%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20existing%20Waqf%20laws%20-%20a%20provision%2C%20he%20said%2C%20that%20allowed%20%26quot%3Bany%20land%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20Waqf%20property%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20opposition%20should%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20spread%20misinformation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20slamming%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20for%20trying%20to%20politicise%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BAppeasement%20does%20not%20lead%20to%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20charge%20is%20significant%2C%20given%20that%20changes%20to%20the%20Waqf%20laws%20comes%20as%20Bihar%20-%20where%20the%20Muslim%20population%20is%20around%2017%20per%20cent%20-%20votes%20in%20an%20Assembly%20election%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20come%20with%20a%20very%20clear%20brief...%20we%20want%20the%20Waqf%20to%20be%20secular%2C%20inclusive%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said%2C%20outlining%20several%20of%20the%20proposed%20changes%2C%20including%20a%20contentious%20rule%20requiring%20two-non%20Muslims%20to%20be%20part%20of%20each%20state%20Waqf%20Board%20and%20the%20central%20Waqf%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20also%20questioned%20the%20lack%20of%20female%20representation%20on%20these%20boards%2C%20declaring%20the%20government%20had%20written%20in%20provisions%20to%20guarantee%20at%20least%20two%20women%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGogoi's%20Rebuttal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20rebuttal%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Gogoi%20referred%20to%20a%20new%20provision%20that%20says%20donations%20to%20Waqf%20boards%20can%20only%20be%20made%20by%20Muslims%20who%20have%20been%20practicing%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProblematic%20clauses%20are%20in%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill...%20it%20is%20sad%20that%20the%20government%20is%20now%20giving%20'religious%20certificates'.%20Will%20they%20seek%20statements%20from%20other%20religions%20also%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20justice%20is%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gogoi%20then%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20of%20trying%20to%20defame%20minority%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20Complains%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20Replies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju's%20fierce%20speech%20was%20preceded%20by%20a%20brief%20ruckus%20as%20NK%20Ramachandran%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Socialist%20Party%20rose%20to%20present%20a%20point%20of%20order.%20He%20questioned%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%20-%20which%20had%20been%20tasked%20last%20year%20with%20reviewing%20the%20original%20Bill%20-%20to%20make%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramachandran%20said%20that%2C%20by%20his%20interpretation%20of%20the%20rules%2C%20the%20JPC%20should%20not%20have%20introduced%20changes%20to%20the%20bill%2C%20as%20it%20had%20not%20been%20expressly%20authorised%20to%20do%20so%20by%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20the%2014%20changes%20(all%20suggested%20by%20MPs%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20or%20allied%20parties%2C%20another%20point%20of%20contention%20with%20the%20opposition)%20that%20had%20been%20made%20by%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20changes%20were%20cleared%20by%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20rose%20for%20a%20brief%20rebuttal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20the%20committee%20-%20led%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Jagadambika%20Pal%20-%20had%20offered%20suggestions%20that%20were%20then%20accepted%20by%20the%20union%20government%20and%20not%20the%20committee%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20Timeline%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20was%20first%20tabled%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20August%20last%20year%20amid%20furious%20protests%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20slammed%20the%20proposed%20law%20as%20%26quot%3Bdraconian%26quot%3B.%20A%20day%20later%20it%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20committee%2C%20which%20filed%20its%20report%20in%20February%20after%20opposition%20MPs%20said%20their%20views%20had%20been%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-joint-parliamentary-committee-mockery-opposition-mps-in-waqf-house-panel-say-their-suggestions-ignored-7585859%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpposition%