%20with%20metallic%20gray%20and%20white%20tones.%20The%20watch%20is%20double-sided%2C%20with%20its%20top%20face%20featuring%20four%20subdials%20and%20its%20inner%20face%20showing%20the%20position%20of%20the%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20telling%20its%20wearer%20the%20time%2C%20the%20watch%20also%20shows%20the%20sun's%20position%2C%20height%2C%20trajectory%2C%20and%20angle%20relative%20to%20the%20Earth.%20It%20also%20lets%20the%20wearer%20know%20which%20constellations%20are%20overhead%20and%20how%20long%20it%20will%20take%20for%20a%20star%20to%20be%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watch%20was%20revealed%20at%20the%20Watches%20and%20Wonders%20trade%20fair%20in%20Geneva%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Vacheron%20Constantin%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20from%20Business%20Insider%20regarding%20the%20retail%20price%20of%20the%20watch%2C%20when%20it%20would%20be%20available%20for%20sale%2C%20and%20how%20many%20pieces%20of%20this%20model%20would%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20watch%20follows%20the%20watchmaker's%20history%20of%20making%20ultra-complicated%20watches.%20In%202024%2C%20it%20released%20the%20%26quot%3BLes%20Cabinotiers%20-%20The%20Berkley%20Grand%20Complication%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20pocketwatch%20with%2063%20complications%20and%202%2C877%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0a1771b-573a-443a-bb8a-d9c79cb5c7a8%5C%22%3E'Extremely%20delicate'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20watch%20with%20this%20many%20complications%20is%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20delicate%2C%26quot%3B%20Altieri%20said.%20Servicing%20would%20likely%20take%20months%20and%20could%20probably%20be%20done%20only%20by%20Vacheron's%20top-level%20master%20watchmakers%20in%20Geneva%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCollectors%20and%20horological%20folks%20will%20worship%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20not%20meant%20for%20mass%20appeal.%20It's%20meant%20as%20a%20show-stopper.%20A%20jaw-dropper%2C%26quot%3B%20Altieri%20s