c%C3%A9e%20Lauren%20Sanchez%20are%20set%20to%20tie%20the%20knot%20in%20Venice%2C%20Italy%2C%20this%20summer%2C%20nearly%20two%20years%20after%20their%20engagement%20in%20May%202023.%20The%20highly%20anticipated%20wedding%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20luxurious%20and%20star-studded%20affair.%20While%20the%20exact%20details%20of%20the%20festivities%20are%20still%20under%20wraps%2C%20it%20is%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20wedding%20of%20the%20century%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20its%20grandeur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Ms%20Sanchez%20started%20dating%20the%20Amazon%20boss%20in%202018.%20The%20couple%20went%20public%20with%20their%20relationship%20on%20July%2014%2C%202019%2C%20after%20Mr%20Bezos'%20divorce%20from%20his%20first%20wife%2C%20MacKenzie%20Scott%2C%20was%20finalised.%C2%A0The%20billionaire%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpagesix.com%2F2023%2F05%2F22%2Fjeff-bezos-engaged-to-lauren-sanchez-after-nearly-5-years-together%2F%5C%22%3Eproposed%20to%20Ms%20Sanchez%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%202023%20while%20sailing%20through%20Europe%20on%20his%20superyacht.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20she%20was%20spotted%20wearing%20a%20massive%20diamond%20engagement%20ring%20on%20her%20finger%2C%20worth%20a%20whopping%20%242.5%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20details%20of%20the%20wedding%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E200%20Guests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20list%20for%20Jeff%20Bezos%20and%20Lauren%20Sanchez's%20wedding%20is%20a%20veritable%20who's%20who%20of%20A-list%20celebrities%20and%20influential%20figures.%20According%20to%20TMZ%2C%20attendees%20will%20include%20Eva%20Longoria%2C%20Katy%20Perry%20and%20Orlando%20Bloom%2C%20Oprah%20and%20Gayle%20King%2C%20Kris%20Jenner%2C%20and%20Kim%20Kardashian.%20The%20guest%20list%20also%20boasts%20some%20prominent%20politicians%20and%20business%20leaders%2C%20such%20as%20Ivanka%20Trump%20and%20Jared%20Kushner%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Joshua%20Kushner%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Karlie%20Kloss.%20Notably%2C%20there's%20no%20official%20word%20on%20whether%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20been%20invited%2C%20but%20given%20Bezos%20and%20Sanchez's%20prominent%20presence%20at%20the%20inauguration%2C%20it's%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20statement%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flive.comune.venezia.it%2Fit%2F2025%2F03%2Fmatrimonio-di-jeff-bezos-venezia-un-grande-evento-nel-rispetto-della-citt-una-nota-dell%5C%22%3EThe%20City%20of%20Venice%C2%A0said%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20200%20guests%20would%20be%20invited%2C%20a%20number%20easily%20accommodated%20without%20any%20disruption%20to%20the%20city%2C%20its%20residents%20and%20visitors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuxury%20Hotels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuxury%20accommodations%20in%20Venice%20are%20being%20snapped%20up%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20wedding.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Ftvshowbiz%2Farticle-14536881%2FALISON-BOSHOFF-Jeff-Bezos-wedding-Venice-George-Clooney.html%5C%22%3EThe%20Daily%20Mail%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20two%20of%20the%20city's%20most%20upscale%20hotels%2C%20Gritti%20Palace%20and%20Aman%20Venice%2C%20are%20fully%20booked%20for%20the%20weekend.%20Room%20rates%20at%20these%20exclusive%20hotels%20range%20from%20%243%2C200%20to%20%2432%2C000%2C%20indicating%20that%20no%20expense%20is%20being%20spared%20for%20the%20couple's%20special%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20local%20news%20outlet%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20preparation%20for%20the%20event%2C%20Venice%20is%20bracing%20for%20the%20arrival%20of%20VIPs.%20The%20city's%20top%20luxury%20hotels%20have%20already%20been%20booked%2C%20and%20reports%20say%20the%20entire%20fleet%20of%20water%20taxis%20will%20be%20made%20available%20to%20shuttle%20guests%20across%20the%20canals.%20The%20logistics%20point%20to%20a%20highly%20exclusive%2C%20tightly%20coordinated%20celebration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBride's%20Extravagant%20Dress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bride%20has%20made%20her%20choice%20for%20the%20perfect%20wedding%20dress%2C%20opting%20for%20a%20design%20from%20the%20renowned%20fashion%20house%20Oscar%20de%20la%20Renta.%20She%20also%20had%20the%20expert%20guidance%20of%20Anna%20Wintour%2C%20the%20influential%20editor-in-chief%20of%20Vogue.%20Ms%20Wintour%20previously%20mentored%20Lauren%20Sanchez%20for%20the%20Met%20Gala%20Ball%2C%20where%20she%20wore%20a%20stunning%20de%20la%20Renta%20gown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20a%20Yacht%20wedding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20initial%20reports%20suggested%20that%20the%20wedding%20would%20take%20place%20aboard%20their%20luxurious%20%24500%20million%20mega%20yacht%2C%20Koru%2C%20sources%20close%20to%20the%20couple%20have%20clarified%20that%20the%20yacht's%20role%20is%20more%20nuanced.%20Instead%20of%20hosting%20the%20ceremony%2C%20the%20yacht%20will%20reportedly%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20celebrations%2C%20perhaps%20by%20taking%20guests%20on%20excursions%20around%20the%20Venetian%20Lagoon%20during%20the%20festivities.%20A%20well-placed%20friend%20has%20confirmed%20that%20the%20wedding%20itself%20will%20not%20be%20held%20on%20the%20boat%2C%20likely%20due%20to%20regulations%20in%20place%20to%20protect%20the%20city.%20A%20yacht%20of%20Koru's%20size%20would%20need%20to%20anchor%20in%20the%20Arsenale%20area%2C%20which%20is%20not%20the%20most%20picturesque%20part%20of%20Venice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743572460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Faauktbag_jeff-bezoslauren-sanchez_625x300_23_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fa-list-guests-exclusive-venues-inside-jeff-bezos-and-lauren-sanchezs-grand-wedding-8066919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20City%20of%20Venice%20said%20only%20200%20guests%20would%20be%